        "content": "<p>The initial implementation of <a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/wasi-tls\">wasi-tls</a> just got <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/10249\">merged</a> into wasmtime <span aria-label=\"octopus\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f419\" role=\"img\" title=\"octopus\">:octopus:</span> <br>\nThanks <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"625613\">@James Sturtevant</span> !</p>\n<p>It is gated behind the <code>-S tls</code> command-line flag.</p>\n<p>Example can be seen <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/blob/e8d5e3ae2bbc1d6816134db189ed472e612563e2/crates/test-programs/src/bin/tls_sample_application.rs\">here</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/wasi-tls\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/0aa1dc6467f33e6b9c7c5bd32982a47d3e55ca67/68747470733a2f2f6f70656e67726170682e6769746875626173736574732e636f6d2f353737366664646333613562346665613230386538383933366434323538333534316664616337396537353032663133323065666665633961666539376436642f576562417373656d626c792f776173692d746c73&quot;)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/wasi-tls\" title=\"GitHub - WebAssembly/wasi-tls: SSL/TLS interface for WASI\">GitHub - WebAssembly/wasi-tls: SSL/TLS interface for WASI</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">SSL/TLS interface for WASI. Contribute to WebAssembly/wasi-tls development by creating an account on GitHub.</div></div></div><div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/10249\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://uploads.zulipusercontent.&quot;)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/10249\" title=\"Initial implementation of Wasi-tls (Transport Layer Security)  